title: The Olivia Tremor Control
description: Hear the band recorded live in concert from (Le) Poisson Rouge in New York City, from Sept. 21, 2011. Set List: Opening A Peculiar Noise Called Train Director I'm Not Feeling Human Memories Of Jacqueline 1906 Define A Transparent Dream Courtyard A Place We Have Been To The Game You Play Is In Your Head Parts 1, 2, 3 Jumping Fences Grass Canons California Demise 3 Green Typewriters (suite) NYC-25 Black Foliage Paranormal Echoes I Have Been Floated No Growing A Sleepy Company Mystery Hideaway The Sylvan Screen Encore: Holiday Surprise 1, 2, 3 The Opera House
